Data Transaction
(1) Miners apply for ID transaction to the Exchange.
(2) Miners apply the ID transaction to the institutions for exchanging link and exchanging ID in the similar exchanging process. exchanging ID can be set to be valid for one or multiple times.
(3) Miners submit the exchanging link, exchanging ID and transaction amount to the Exchange, which only shows the exchanging link. This link can only browse for non-privacy information, such as position information in the organization, etc. 
(4) After the transaction is finished, another party can obtain the exchanging ID, and the organization completes the exchanging ID activation according to the transaction ID.
